ts feature insert knowledge base link and predefined reply will be shown with dropdown with ability to search.<\/li>\n<li>Improved: Calendar for admin and customers area will be ajax based to improve loading time.<\/li>\n<li>Improved: Totally rewrited tables SQL queries for tables that is possible large amount to exist for faster performance.<\/li>\n<li>Improved: As download pdf name for proposals will be used proposal number like invoices and estimates.<\/li>\n<li>Improved: Allowed payment modes for invoice will be shown as multi select instead of checkboxes.<\/li>\n<li>Improved: Design and alignments.<\/li>\n<li>Improved: When searching projects in dropdown, the project ID will be shown is number as unique identifier.<\/li>\n<li>Improved: Combined few css and javascript files into one for better performance in admin area.<\/li>\n<li>Updated Portugese brazil translation &#8211; Thanks to\u00a0<a href=\"http:\/\/webserra.com.br\/\">http:\/\/webserra.com.br\/<\/a><\/li>\n<li>Updated French translation.<\/li>\n<li>Update Russian translation.<\/li>\n<li>Updated Codeigniter Framework to 3.1.5 version.<\/li>\n<li>Fixed task tags not working properly sometimes.<\/li>\n<li>Fixed cant upload some file extensions in media even its the extension is allowed from the settings.<\/li>\n<li>Fixed Authorize.net not showing error messages.<\/li>\n<li>Fixed Mollie payments not updating, issue with Mollie server ip change.<\/li>\n<li>Fixed problem with password encryption in customer vault when special characters exists.<\/li>\n<li>Fixed columns in customer profile for contracts not correct when custom fields exists.<\/li>\n<li>Fixed proposals not correct in customers area calendar.<\/li>\n<li>Fixed custom fields for single task not shown in customers area.<\/li>\n<li>Fixed when sending project file to email attachment filename is empty.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>\u00a0 Important notes: Re-check all your my_ prefix files. If you are using your own t